590
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:07,030
Izinkan saya menarik napas.

591
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,880
Kau bantu aku mengutuk bajingan pengecut itu

592
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:09,640
